SELECT sales_order_id AS id, sales_order_status AS status, sales_order_price AS price, sales_order_customer_id AS customer_id, sales_order_customer_name AS customer_name, sales_order_customer_address AS customer_address, sales_order_customer_no_handphone AS customer_no_handphone, sales_order_date AS date, sales_order_proof AS proof FROM `sales_order` WHERE sales_order_status = 'payed' AND sales_order_id = 66
